{"ts":"2026-04-07T09:23:45.471Z","tool":"execute_code","type":"tool","status":"SUCCESS","ms":733,"action":"execute","params":{"action":"execute","code":"\n// Add GameHUD, PauseMenu, GameOverScreen to the scene\nvar managers = GameObject.Find(\"--- MANAGERS ---\");\n\n// Create GameplayUI object\nvar uiGO = new GameObject(\"GameplayUI\");\nuiGO.transform.SetParent(managers.transform);\n\n// Add components\nvar hudType = System.Type.GetType(\"FightForLife.UI.GameHUD, Assembly-CSharp\");\nvar pauseType = System.Type.GetType(\"FightForLife.UI.PauseMenu, Assembly-CSharp\");\nvar goType = System.Type.GetType(\"FightForLife.UI.GameOverScreen, Assembly-CSharp\");\n\nvar result = \"\";\nif (hudType != null) { uiGO.AddComponent(hudType); result += \"GameHUD added\\n\"; }\nif (pauseType != null) { uiGO.AddComponent(pauseType); result += \"PauseMenu added\\n\"; }\nif (goType != null) { uiGO.AddComponent(goType); result += \"GameOverScreen added\\n\"; }\n\n// Save\nUnityEditor.SceneManagement.EditorSceneManager.MarkSceneDirty(\n    UnityEditor.SceneManagement.EditorSceneManager.GetActiveScene());\nUnityEditor.SceneManagement.EditorSceneManager.SaveOpenScenes();\n\nreturn result + \"Scene saved!\";\n","safety_checks":true,"compiler":"auto"}}
