{"ts":"2026-04-07T09:24:10.391Z","tool":"execute_code","type":"tool","status":"SUCCESS","ms":1512,"action":"execute","params":{"action":"execute","code":"\n// Save current scene, then update MainMenu scene to have MainMenuController\nUnityEditor.SceneManagement.EditorSceneManager.SaveOpenScenes();\n\n// Open MainMenu scene additively to add the controller\nvar mainMenuScene = UnityEditor.SceneManagement.EditorSceneManager.OpenScene(\n    \"Assets/_FightForLife/Scenes/MainMenu.unity\",\n    UnityEditor.SceneManagement.OpenSceneMode.Single\n);\n\n// Check if MainMenuController already exists\nvar existingControllers = GameObject.FindObjectsOfType<MonoBehaviour>(true);\nbool hasController = false;\nvar controllerType = AssetDatabase.LoadAssetAtPath<MonoScript>(\"Assets/_FightForLife/Scripts/UI/MainMenuController.cs\").GetClass();\n\nforeach (var mb in existingControllers)\n{\n    if (mb.GetType() == controllerType)\n    {\n        hasController = true;\n        break;\n    }\n}\n\nvar result = $\"MainMenu scene loaded. Has controller: {hasController}\\n\";\n\nif (!hasController)\n{\n    // Find the MainCanvas or create a controller object\n    var canvas = GameObject.Find(\"MainCanvas\");\n    if (canvas != null)\n    {\n        canvas.AddComponent(controllerType);\n        result += \"Added MainMenuController to MainCanvas\\n\";\n    }\n    else\n    {\n        var go = new GameObject(\"MainMenuController\");\n        go.AddComponent(controllerType);\n        result += \"Created MainMenuController object\\n\";\n    }\n}\n\n// Save\nUnityEditor.SceneManagement.EditorSceneManager.MarkSceneDirty(mainMenuScene);\nUnityEditor.SceneManagement.EditorSceneManager.SaveOpenScenes();\n\n// Go back to Island_Flood\nUnityEditor.SceneManagement.EditorSceneManager.OpenScene(\n    \"Assets/_FightForLife/Scenes/Island_Flood.unity\",\n    UnityEditor.SceneManagement.OpenSceneMode.Single\n);\n\nreturn result + \"Done! Back on Island_Flood.\";\n","safety_checks":false,"compiler":"auto"}}
